thread.title: Ms Cleo de Vito
thread.title_full: 25Plus reviewed by Ms Cleo de Vito

author: Ms Cleo de Vito
title: Ms Cleo de Vito
text: Hate that we have to phone to add a garage loan car to our insurance, & that costs as well. Whilst everyone appears nice on the phone, they never seem able to provide the service you ask for. And hate that our insurance continues to rise - despite that we have not claimed in more than 10 years, & our car is growing older as well.
